‘Evil Came’: The Toll of Russia’s Occupation in Kyiv’s Suburbs

Residents of Bucha, Borodyanka and Hostomel, suburbs of Ukraine’s capital, describe the horrors left behind by Russian forces: land mines, bullet-riddled cars and corpses lying in the street. Watch the full video

